## Agent Routing (agentHint) - CRITICAL

**EVERY task MUST have a valid `agentHint` set.** Do NOT leave it empty or default everything to "rex".

| Agent | `agentHint` Value | Keywords to Match | Examples |
|-------|-------------------|-------------------|----------|
| **Bolt** | `"bolt"` | infrastructure, deploy, kubernetes, k8s, database, postgresql, redis, kafka, storage, provision, operator, cluster, helm | "Provision PostgreSQL", "Deploy Kafka cluster", "Setup Redis cache" |
| **Rex** | `"rex"` | rust, axum, tokio, cargo, backend (when rust specified), sqlx | "Implement Rust API", "Build axum service", "Create tokio worker" |
| **Grizz** | `"grizz"` | go, golang, grpc, chi, protobuf, go-based | "Go microservice", "gRPC API", "Chi router" |
| **Nova** | `"nova"` | node, nodejs, bun, elysia, effect, drizzle, typescript backend, express, nestjs, hono | "Bun API", "Elysia service", "Node.js worker", "TypeScript API" |
| **Blaze** | `"blaze"` | react, nextjs, next.js, frontend, web ui, dashboard, admin panel, web app, shadcn, tailwind, component | "React dashboard", "Next.js app", "Admin UI", "Web frontend" |
| **Tap** | `"tap"` | expo, react native, mobile, ios, android, mobile app | "Mobile app", "Expo app", "React Native screen" |
| **Spark** | `"spark"` | electron, desktop, desktop app, tauri | "Desktop app", "Electron client" |
| **Tess** | `"tess"` | test suite, testing, e2e test, qa, coverage | "Write test suite", "E2E testing" |
| **Cipher** | `"cipher"` | security audit, vulnerability, auth review | "Security audit", "Penetration test" |
| **Atlas** | `"atlas"` | merge, integrate all, combine PRs | "Final integration" |

### Agent Assignment Rules

1. **Task 1 = ALWAYS Bolt** - Infrastructure must be provisioned first
2. **Backend API without language specified → Ask PRD or default to Nova** (TypeScript is most common)
3. **"Dashboard", "Admin Panel", "Web App" → Blaze** (these are frontend even if they have "admin" in name)
4. **"API" alone is NOT enough** - look for language hints (Rust → Rex, Go → Grizz, Node/Bun → Nova)
5. **When PRD specifies stack** - e.g., "(Nova - Bun/Elysia)" in title → use that agent

### Common Mistakes to Avoid

| Wrong | Right | Reason |
|-------|-------|--------|
| `"agentHint": "rex"` for "Admin Dashboard" | `"agentHint": "blaze"` | Dashboard = frontend |
| `"agentHint": "rex"` for "Setup PostgreSQL" | `"agentHint": "bolt"` | Database setup = infrastructure |
| `"agentHint": "rex"` for "Bun API Service" | `"agentHint": "nova"` | Bun = Node.js ecosystem |
| `"agentHint": "rex"` for "gRPC Gateway" | `"agentHint": "grizz"` | gRPC typically = Go |
| `"agentHint": null` | Always set a value | Never leave empty |

