## Quality Checklist

Before finalizing, verify EVERY item:

- [ ] **Task 1 is `agentHint: "bolt"`** - Infrastructure MUST be first
- [ ] **Every task has `agentHint` set** - No null or empty values
- [ ] **Agent hints match task type:**
  - [ ] Frontend/Dashboard/UI tasks → `blaze`
  - [ ] Infrastructure/Database/K8s tasks → `bolt`
  - [ ] Rust tasks → `rex`
  - [ ] Go/gRPC tasks → `grizz`
  - [ ] Node/Bun/TypeScript API tasks → `nova`
  - [ ] Mobile/Expo tasks → `tap`
  - [ ] Desktop/Electron tasks → `spark`
- [ ] Every task has non-empty `details` with PRD context embedded
- [ ] Every task has non-empty `testStrategy` with specific verification commands
- [ ] Dependencies form valid DAG (no cycles)
- [ ] Implementation tasks depend on task-001 (infrastructure)
- [ ] Frontend tasks depend on their backend API tasks
- [ ] Each task is atomic (completable in one PR)

**STOP and review if most tasks are assigned to Rex** - this usually indicates incorrect routing.

